In this task, I built a Natural Language Processing pipeline to classify customer reviews as positive or negative. I first cleaned and tokenized the text data by converting it to lowercase and removing unwanted characters. The cleaned text was converted into numerical features using TF-IDF vectorization. I trained a Logistic Regression model to classify the reviews and evaluated its performance using accuracy, classification report, and confusion matrix. Finally, I saved the trained model and vectorizer for future use. This task helped me understand how text data can be processed and transformed into meaningful features for machine learning models.